# alchemyGasManagerMiddleware

Alchemy gas manager middleware used as the paymaster middleware overrides param to the client middleware config

## Import

```ts
import { alchemyGasManagerMiddleware } from "@account-kit/infra";
```

## Parameters

### client

`ClientWithAlchemyMethods`
client with alchemy methods

### config

`AlchemyGasManagerConfig`
alchemy gas manager configuration

## Returns

`Pick<ClientMiddlewareConfig,"paymasterAndData" | "feeEstimator" | "gasEstimator">`
the gas estimator, fee estimator, and paymasterAndData middleware for Alchemy gas manager
